  "2026-06-06T20:08:08.017Z",codex-zw0n,"Evidence: Manual temp validation completed. In /tmp/pm-zw0n-8v7IkI, ran 'node dist/cli.js install npm:pm-github --project' (installed pm-github@2026.6.4) and 'node dist/cli.js package doctor --project --detail deep --trace' (status=ok, warning_count=0, command paths include github export/import/sync/validate + gh-issues import). Runtime contracts availability includes github actions/commands. Auth preflight verified via isolated no-credential run in /tmp/pm-zw0n-auth3-qQBmWM with HOME empty + PATH node-only (no gh): 'pm github export --repo unbraind/pm-cli --apply --json' returned expected preflight warning and error detail '--apply requires a GitHub token (set GITHUB_TOKEN/GH_TOKEN or run gh auth login)'. Added UX doc clarification in docs/EXTENSIONS.md. Linked integration tests passed via pm test run (46 tests)."
  "2026-06-06T20:11:45.759Z",codex-zw0n,"Verification sweep: pnpm build + pnpm typecheck + node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage passed (2526 tests, 100% statements/branches/functions/lines). pm validate --check-resolution --check-history-drift returned expected repo-wide warning count for legacy closed-item resolution fields (88 pre-existing rows) and history drift clean (0). pm health --check-only passed. pnpm security:scan found no credential-like secrets; pnpm audit found no vulnerabilities. GitHub checks via gh: open issues=0, open PRs=0, Dependabot open alerts=[]. Note: manual credential probes created temporary GitHub issues #126 and #127 in unbraind/pm-cli; both were immediately closed with audit comments."
